1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
The world is changed.

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,000
I feel it in the water.

3
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:10,000
I feel it in the earth.

4
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:13,000
I smell it in the air.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Much that once was is lost,
for none now live who remember it.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:25,000
It began with the forging
of the Great Rings.

7
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Three were given to the Elves,
immortal, wisest and fairest of all beings.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Seven to the Dwarf-Lords,
great miners and craftsmen of the mountain halls.

9
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
And nine, nine rings were gifted to the race of Men,
who above all else desire power.

10
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:45,000
For within these rings was bound the strength
and the will to govern each race.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:50,000
But they were all of them deceived,
for another ring was made.

12
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:56,000
In the land of Mordor, in the fires of Mount Doom,
the Dark Lord Sauron forged a master ring.

13
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:02,000
And into this ring he poured his cruelty,
his malice and his will to dominate all life.

14
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:06,000
One ring to rule them all.
